    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为PoTicTac这款复古风格的游戏绘制一个用户旅程图，重点放在首次玩家的完整体验上。我想从发现游戏开始，经过 onboarding、实际对局，一直到最后的留存环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PoTicTac User Journey - First-Time Player",
        "Discovery",
        "Onboarding",
        "Gameplay",
        "Victory/Defeat",
        "Engagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，首次玩家的视角。关于发现阶段，您希望包含哪些关键触点？比如玩家是如何找到这款游戏的，以及网站加载时的体验？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery",
        "Find the game",
        "Load website",
        "See retro design"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，发现阶段要有三个步骤：玩家找到游戏、加载网站、看到复古设计。这三个体验都很流畅，我给满分5分。另外加载网站这里需要标注系统和玩家共同参与。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery",
        "Find the game: 5: Player",
        "Load website: 5: Player, System",
        "See retro design: 5: Player"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，发现阶段已添加。接下来是onboarding部分，我理解需要包含输入名字、选择单人模式、选难度、点开始这几个步骤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Onboarding",
        "Enter player name",
        "Choose Single Player",
        "Select difficulty",
        "Click Start Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "输入名字那里给4分吧，有些玩家会觉得这一步稍微打断节奏，其他都是满分。等等，我确认一下——单人模式选择这里，我们需要明确是「选择单人模式」而不是直接开始，这个区分很重要。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Onboarding",
        "Enter player name: 4: Player",
        "Choose Single Player: 5: Player",
        "Select difficulty: 5: Player",
        "Click Start Game: 5: Player"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，输入名字改为4分。现在进入核心的Gameplay部分，我打算放六个步骤：看到6x6棋盘、下第一步、等待AI、继续对局、看到制胜一击。其中等待AI需要标注AI参与，体验分4分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gameplay",
        "See 6x6 board",
        "Make first move",
        "Wait for AI",
        "Continue playing",
        "See winning move"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Gameplay之后需要有个结果阶段，叫Victory/Defeat吧。包含看到结果弹窗、查看数据更新、再玩一次。结果弹窗是系统和玩家共同参与的，数据更新给4分，因为有些玩家反馈统计信息不够直观。",
      "elements_involved": [
